{"tid":1439105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾鎮濤: 金錢破產並非末路 人格破產才是絕境","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T02:50:13.000Z","uid":297241,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ba670b3f3075002d0b8c79f7b5257f4ba31f9997","tid":1439105,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"鍾鎮濤昨日正式向法庭申請破產後，隨即往深圳秘密拍攝新片，他未有受破產事件影響心情，更傳真表示今日會召開記者會交代事件，傳真中更有16字真言，深信<span style=\"color: red;\">金錢破產並非末路，人格破產才是絕境。 </span><br />\n<br />\n因投資豪宅失利，鍾鎮濤及章小蕙共欠下裕泰興公司二億五千萬，章小蕙早前被該公司入稟追討欠款。鍾鎮濤昨天已正式向法庭申請破產，若獲法庭接納，他會被免除償還欠債，而章小蕙就要獨力承擔全部欠款。"},{"pid":"536dbdc05c96141a1b3b47c5db5f01c187b28102","tid":1439105,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"131622b67dd6da5ce2197b8124c72804bc8ea6c9","tid":1439105,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"要個女人獨力承擔欠款都唔叫人格破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7461a40132565174a702e67cca748ef00f0c939","tid":1439105,"uid":39269,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"鍾生你兩樣都冇"},{"pid":"503ab18b8659db24713f3d1d12c1d83b5a224614","tid":1439105,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"呢條友人格都唔多好啦"},{"pid":"915533d13542dd87e362f6e23377d61a86a7c635","tid":1439105,"uid":58353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，呢條友又破產<br />\n有仔女就咪撚玩咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkT2PrV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkT2PrV.png&h=a5a35de4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"348b919c0a40cbf09ce3f26ac197434f62e076ef","tid":14